## 步骤 11：加载与比较（如果之前的回顾存在）

检查 `.agents/retros/` 中是否有之前的回顾快照：

如果存在，进行比较：
```
TREND vs LAST RETRO
═══════════════════════════════════════
  Metric          Last    Current  Trend
  Commits         25      32       ↑ +28%
  LOC/session     180     220      ↑ +22%
  Test ratio      35%     42%      ↑ +7pp
  Focus score     70%     85%      ↑ +15pp
═══════════════════════════════════════
```

