## 步骤 12：保存快照

将回顾数据保存到 `.agents/retros/{YYYY-MM-DD}.json`：

```json
{
  "date": "YYYY-MM-DD",
  "window_days": 7,
  "commits": N,
  "loc_added": N,
  "loc_removed": N,
  "test_ratio": 0.42,
  "active_days": N,
  "sessions": N,
  "focus_score": 0.85,
  "streak_current": N,
  "streak_best": N,
  "hotspots": ["file1", "file2"],
  "pr_sizes": {"small": N, "medium": N, "large": N, "xl": N}
}
```

